p: Silencing circRAB11FIP1 suppressed the autophagic flux of SKOV3 cells. However, the overexpression of ATG14 or ATG7, or transfection of SKOV3 cells with miR-129 inhibitors, reversed this phenomenon (Fig. 6A, B). CircRAB11FIP1 ectopic expression enhanced the autophagic flux in A2780 cells; however, the silencing of ATG14 or ATG7, or transfection with miR-129 mimics, reversed this phenomenon (Fig. 6C, D).
